file.name: api-with-types.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: API with Types
  version: ""
paths:
  "/users/{id}":
    get:
      operationId: GET_users-id
      responses:
        "200":
          description: ""
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/User"
    parameters:
      - in: path
        name: id
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
components:
  schemas:
    User:
      type: object
      properties:
        firstName:
          type: string
        lastName:
          type: string
        age:
          minimum: 0
          maximum: 99
          type: integer
      required:
        - firstName
        - lastName
        - age
